OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783925469
OL,3,CBody of man recovered from reservoir
OL,5,FThe body of a man has been recovered
OL,6,Ffrom a reservoir following a major
OL,7,Fsearch operation.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FSykes Reservoir in Alexandra Park,
OL,11,FStockport, on the evening of Thursday,
OL,12,F9 July, after reports a man had got
OL,13,Finto difficulty in the water.
OL,15,FWhilst formal identification has yet
OL,16,Fto take place, specialist officers are
OL,17,Fsupporting, Greater Manchester Police
OL,18,F(GMP) said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
