OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783925469
OL,3,CBody of man recovered from reservoir
OL,5,FIssued by the UK Health Security
OL,6,FAgency (UKHSA) in partnership with the
OL,7,FMet Office, the warning was escalated
OL,8,Ffrom yellow to amber on Thursday, 9
OL,9,FJuly, as temperatures continue to
OL,10,Fclimb across the region.
OL,12,FThe amber status indicates that the
OL,13,Fhigh temperatures could have
OL,14,Fsignificant impacts across the health
OL,15,Fand social care sector, posing
OL,16,Fincreased risks to vulnerable people
OL,17,Fand those with pre-existing health
OL,18,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
